               <p>19. 
               
                  <persName id="t17351015-14-defend133" type="defendantName">
                     John 
                     Burton 
                  <interp inst="t17351015-14-defend133" type="surname" value="Burton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17351015-14-defend133" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17351015-14-defend133" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17351015-14-off53" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17351015-14-off53" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17351015-14-off53" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               marrying 
                     
                        <persName id="t17351015-14-victim135" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Simmer 
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim135" type="surname" value="Simmer"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim135" type="given" value="Elizabeth"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim135" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , <rs id="t17351015-14-cd54" type="crimeDate">Dec. 3. 1733</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17351015-14-off53 t17351015-14-cd54"></join>, his former <rs id="t17351015-14-viclabel55" type="occupation">Wife</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17351015-14-victim137 t17351015-14-viclabel55"></join>, 
                     
                        <persName id="t17351015-14-victim137" type="victimName">
                           Ann 
                           Clark 
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim137" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim137" type="given" value="Ann"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17351015-14-victim137" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                      
                   being then living
            </rs>. The Prisoner did not deny the Marriage, but said that his first Wife poxt him in the Wedding Week, and then run away with his Goods. That when she married him, she had another Husband living, and has since married a third. <rs id="t17351015-14-verdict56" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17351015-14-verdict56" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
